<section id="system" class="visio-system">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center">
      <h2>What is Visio Relief?</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">A gentle, effective 4-step system to transform mental fog into clarity and purpose</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="system-steps">
      <div class="system-step">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="step-details">
          <h3>Clarity</h3>
          <p>Identify thought patterns that create mental fog and learn techniques to observe your mind without becoming entangled in its stories. This awareness creates the space needed for transformation.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="system-step">
        <div class="step-number">2</div>
        <div class="step-details">
          <h3>Reconnect</h3>
          <p>Rediscover your connection to your authentic self through guided practices that bypass the critical mind and access your intuitive wisdom. Rebuild trust in your inner guidance system.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="system-step">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="step-details">
          <h3>Focus</h3>
          <p>Learn to direct your attention with purpose and intention. Develop practical tools to maintain mental clarity in challenging situations and make decisions aligned with your values.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="system-step">
        <div class="step-number">4</div>
        <div class="step-details">
          <h3>Reset</h3>
          <p>Integrate these new mental patterns into your daily life through customized rituals and practices. Create sustainable change that grows stronger with time and transforms how you experience life.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="system-summary text-center">
      <p>This gentle yet powerful approach creates lasting change by working with your mind's natural tendencies rather than fighting against them.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="button">Experience the Visio Relief System</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .visio-system {
    background-color: var(--color-background);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .visio-system::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, var(--color-primary-light) 0%, transparent 30%);
    opacity: 0.05;
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  .section-intro {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-xxl);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
  }
  
  .system-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xxl);
  }
  
  .system-step {
    background-color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    position: relative;
    transition: transform var(--transition-medium);
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .system-step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  
  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -20px;
    left: 20px;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }
  
  .system-summary {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .system-summary p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .system-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>